body:
Hey everyone, OPTOBAT here and what we have below is a Top 20 chart on the 20 most subscribed YouTube channels that have at least 1 Avicus video on them.
TAKE NOTE: This is a statistical chart and NOT my personal opinion, so no hate.
Here they are! One last thing, I hate to have to add this but could you guys please take a moment to take a look at my channel and maybe like and subscribe if you like what you see :)
OPTOBAT <-----

#1TheRockmanGamer - 8,296 SUBSCRIBERS! (Holy Crap!)
#2 LegoSean9 | Minecraft PvP | Road To 2k - 2,017 Subscribers!
#3 SilentBlo W- 1,490 Subscribers!
#4 Cals YT - 1,275 Subscribers! 
#5 MinecraftGamerz92 - 1,094 Subscribers!
#6 DivinanceMC - 1,047 Subscribers!
#7 Matic Gaming - Great HD Gaming Videos! - 385 Subscribers :D
#8 cinnamon croc 
#9 MLGPorky - 356 Subscribers :D
#10 Upsoar - 343 Subscribers :D
#11 Zed ther - 278 Subscribers :)
#12 InfernusJono | Road to 500 Subs - 229 Subscribers :)
#13 10theawesomeperson - 215 Subscribers :)    
#14  The Avicus Network - 206 Subscribers :) 
#15 ViolentBooGaming  - 204 Subscribers :) 
#16 QFrog- 172 Subscribers :)
#17 vladthegreat100 - 154 Subscribers :)
#18 SetoGolem - 153 Subscribers :)
#19 Ducksfanwaterloo - 151 Subscribers :)
#20 Theo LP - 146 Subscribers

#33 OPTOBAT - 36 Subscribers :p

Thanks for reading this list guys, but please just keep reading here, because i would just like to explain something here; This list wasn't to prove anything about MY opinion or to show who is best, people like MLGPorky with 250 Subscribers has the passion of someone like PewDiePie with 27 million Subscribers or something like that, so the point is, the numbers next to these people don't mean they are my favourites, and it doesn't mean i hate them either, I'm just saying its about the passion and effort you show.
I just got a bit bored and decided to see who was where in the Top 20 :D

Thanks guys - OPTOBAT
